#. DmbfV
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:128
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Use Data ▸ Statistics for sampling, descriptive statistics, analysis of variance, correlation, and much more in %PRODUCTNAME Calc."
