#. BcK3A
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:132
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "You can show formulas instead of results with View ▸ Show Formula (or Tools ▸ Options ▸ %PRODUCTNAME Calc ▸ View ▸ Display ▸ Formulas)."
