#. Bs9w9
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:135
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Want your chapter titles to always begin a page? Edit Heading1 (paragraph style) ▸ Text Flow ▸ Breaks and check Insert ▸ Page ▸ Before."
