#. XDhNo
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:138
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Use column or row labels in formulas. For example, if you have two columns, “Time” and “KM”, use =Time/KM to get minutes per kilometer."
