#. E7GZz
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:139
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Annoyed by the “marching ants” around cells in Calc? Press escape to stop them; the copied content will remain available for pasting."
