#. GSVYQ
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:155
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Writer lets you number your footnotes per page, chapter, document: Tools ▸ Footnotes and Endnotes ▸ Footnotes tab ▸ Counting."
