#. ALczh
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:158
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Want to insert a value in the same place on several sheets? Select the sheets: hold down %MOD1 key and click their tabs before entering."
