#. qAVmk
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:230
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Need to move a Writer table? Table ▸ Select ▸ Table and Insert ▸ Frame ▸ Frame and move where you want."
