#. TmaSP
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:231
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "With Tools ▸ AutoText ▸ AutoText ▸ Import you can select a Word document or a template containing the AutoText entries that you want to import."
