#. wAFRP
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:235
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Delete all of your printing areas in one step: select all sheets, then Format ▸ Print Ranges ▸ Clear."
