#. khFDu
#: cui/inc/tipoftheday.hrc:237
msgctxt "RID_CUI_TIPOFTHEDAY"
msgid "Having trouble pasting text from PDF files or webpages into documents? Try to paste as unformatted text (%MOD1+%MOD2+Shift+V)."
